威廉佈雷克寫的《無邪的預言》
William Blake. Auguries of Innocence.

702
00:48:57,684 --> 00:48:58,844
你們有嗎？
Think you got it?

703
00:48:58,919 --> 00:49:00,284
我想我們有
Yeah, we should have.

704
00:49:00,353 --> 00:49:03,083
