706
00:49:06,093 --> 00:49:07,617
心理學系…
TEMP: Psychology Department...

707
00:49:07,694 --> 00:49:09,423
芝加哥大學布魯博士辦公室
University of Chicago. Dr. Bloom's office.

708
00:49:09,496 --> 00:49:12,522
嗨，這裡是巴伯和艾德華出版社
Hi. This is Bob Greer at Blaine and Edwards Publishing.

709
00:49:12,632 --> 00:49:15,760
布魯博士要我寄《心理學家與法律》這本書…
Dr. Bloom asked me to send The Psychiatrist and the Law...

710
00:49:15,836 --> 00:49:17,030
給威爾葛蘭姆
to Will Graham.

711
00:49:17,104 --> 00:49:19,595
他的助理原本應該給我…
His assistant was supposed to give me...

712
00:49:19,673 --> 00:49:22,665
地址和電話，但是該死，她沒給
the address and phone number, but, darn it, she never did.

713
00:49:22,776 --> 00:49:25,540
我只是臨時僱員，琳達星期一會來上班
TEMP: I'm just a temp. Linda will be in on Monday.

714
00:49:25,645 --> 00:49:28,341
再過五分鐘，聯邦快遞就來了
I have to catch FedEx in about five minutes.

715
