我不想麻煩布魯博士
I hate to bother Dr. Bloom about it...

716
00:49:30,016 --> 00:49:31,881
因為他告訴琳達要寄出去…
because he told Linda to send it...

717
00:49:31,952 --> 00:49:34,045
我不想讓琳達惹上麻煩
and I don't want to get her into trouble.

718
00:49:34,121 --> 00:49:36,885
地址就在桌上的名片夾裡
It's right there in the Rolodex, or whatever.

719
00:49:36,990 --> 00:49:39,823
如果你願意告訴我，我會在你的婚禮上跳舞
I'll dance at your wedding if you read it to me.

720
00:49:39,893 --> 00:49:42,828
我不知道，我真的不應該這樣做的
TEMP: I don't know. I'm really not supposed to.

721
00:49:42,896 --> 00:49:45,194
行行好，只要翻翻名片夾…
Be a darling and flip that old rascal...

722
00:49:45,298 --> 00:49:47,061
我不會多耽誤你的時間
I won't take up any more of your time.

723
00:49:47,134 --> 00:49:49,329
葛蘭姆…威爾
Graham, Will.

724
00:49:50,403 --> 00:49:52,496
好，等一下
TEMP: All right. Just a minute.

725
00:49:54,374 --> 00:49:56,808
葛蘭姆
"Gibson, Gordon, Graham."

726
00:49:56,877 --> 00:49:58,401
這裡沒有住家地址
It doesn't give a home address.

727
00:49:58,478 --> 00:49:59,911
那有什麼，親愛的？
What does it have, dear?

728
00:49:59,980 --> 00:50:02,208
「FBI，華盛頓特區，西北區…」
TEMP: "FBI, 935 Pennsylvania Avenue Northwest, Washington, D.C."

729
00:50:02,220 --> 00:50:04,508
「賓夕法尼亞大道93號」

730
00:50:04,584 --> 00:50:06,552
是嗎？　　我看看
LECTER: Yeah? TEMP: And let's see.

731
00:50:07,487 --> 00:50:08,920
在這裡
Here it is.

732
00:50:08,989 --> 00:50:12,891
「郵政信箱3680，馬拉松，佛羅里達」
"P.O. Box 3680, Marathon, Florida."

733
00:50:13,059 --> 00:50:14,959
馬拉松   對
LECTER: Marathon. TEMP: Yes.

734
00:50:15,662 --> 00:50:18,358
這樣就夠了，你是我的天使
That's fine. You're an angel.

735
