（女人以陽光為服）

739
00:50:45,792 --> 00:50:50,456
（純色色彩實驗室）

740
00:51:06,313 --> 00:51:08,474
（紅外線感光材質使用中）

741
00:51:12,586 --> 00:51:14,554
我是弗朗西斯杜爾
I'm Francis Dolarhyde.

742
00:51:15,088 --> 00:51:17,648
我是來拿紅外線包裹的
I've come for the package of infrared.

743
00:51:17,757 --> 00:51:20,783
把你的背貼著牆往前…
Right. Put your back against the door and come...

744
00:51:21,094 --> 00:51:23,961
走三步，直到你感覺腳下有磁磚
forward three steps till you feel tile under your feet.

745
00:51:24,064 --> 00:51:26,396
就在左手邊…有一個凳子
And there's a stool just on the left.

746
00:51:28,568 --> 00:51:32,129
一樣是技術服務部門的杜先生，對不對？
Same Mr. D who's head of Tech Services, am I right?

747
00:51:33,139 --> 00:51:35,107
我是麗巴瑪凱蓮
I'm Reba McClane.

748
00:51:35,508 --> 00:51:38,807
再等一下下，我就把燈打開
Just a second more and I will get you some light.

749
00:51:41,615 --> 00:51:43,776
好啦
REBA: Okay, here we go.

750
00:51:48,355 --> 00:51:50,789
告訴我，你要紅外線做什麼？
So, what do you need the IR for?

751
00:51:51,958 --> 00:51:53,721
是動物園要
It's for the zoo.

752
00:51:53,827 --> 00:51:56,591
他們想拍下夜間動物的照片
They want to photograph the nocturnal animals.

753
00:51:56,663 --> 00:52:01,100
太好了，我喜歡動物，不過我要警告你
That's great. I love animals. I got to warn you, though.

754
00:52:01,368 --> 00:52:05,964
這個東西要很小心，沒拿好會受傷的
This stuff is pretty sensitive. It can be mean to handle.

755
00:52:08,608 --> 00:52:11,543
但是我應該不用告訴你這些
But I guess I don't need to tell you that.

756
00:52:19,552 --> 00:52:23,113
嘿，麗巴，哦，杜爾先生，哇！
Hey, Reba. Oh, Mr. D. Whoa!

757
00:52:23,823 --> 00:52:26,291
我沒打攪你們吧，有嗎？
I'm not interrupting anything, am I?

758
00:52:26,359 --> 00:52:27,792
沒有，洛夫
No, Ralph.

759
00:52:27,861 --> 00:52:29,692
外面開始下雨了
It's starting to spritz outside.

760
00:52:29,763 --> 00:52:31,128
載你好嗎？
I'll give you a lift home?

761
00:52:31,197 --> 00:52:32,824
你騎摩托車
You ride a motorcycle.

762
00:52:32,899 --> 00:52:35,129
怎麼幫我躲雨？
How's that gonna help me with the rain?

763
00:52:35,201 --> 00:52:37,863
我想也許我們可以到哪裡…
I thought maybe we'd stop off someplace...

764
00:52:38,004 --> 00:52:39,995
小喝一杯
have ourselves a little sundowner.

765
00:52:40,073 --> 00:52:42,906
有人會來載我   酷
- I've already got a ride. - It's cool.

766
00:52:43,410 --> 00:52:46,846
很好，沒問題
That's cool. No problemo.

767
00:52:55,989 --> 00:52:59,755
如果有比同情還讓人討厭的東西，那就是假同情
If there's anything I hate worse than pity, it's fake pity.

768
00:52:59,859 --> 00:53:03,260
特別是像洛夫曼第這樣卑鄙的人
Especially from a walking hard-on like Ralph Mandy.

769
00:53:04,331 --> 00:53:07,528
對不起   我沒有同情心
- Sorry. - I have no pity.

770
00:53:41,801 --> 00:53:43,496
我載你！
Ride with me!

771
00:53:44,204 --> 00:53:47,071
謝謝，我習慣搭公交車
Thanks, but I take the bus all the time.

772
00:53:49,042 --> 00:53:52,136
曼第是個白癡，能載你…
Mandy is a fool. Ride with me...

773
00:53:54,681 --> 00:53:56,444
…是我的榮幸
for my pleasure.

774
00:54:10,330 --> 00:54:13,231
你要進來嗎？我們喝點東西
You want to come in? I'll fix us a drink.

775
00:54:19,606 --> 00:54:22,939
也許下一次   我進去
- Maybe another time. - I will come in.

776
00:54:31,184 --> 00:54:33,618
動物園的計劃什麼時候開始？
When is the zoo project?

777
00:54:33,887 --> 00:54:36,670
也許下個禮拜他們會打電話給我
- Maybe next week. They'll call. - I love zoos.

778
00:54:36,687 --> 00:54:37,880
我愛動物園

779
00:54:39,692 --> 00:54:44,026
事實上我很早的記憶是，我看過美洲獅…
In fact one of my earliest memories is seeing a cougar...

780
00:54:44,597 --> 00:54:46,531
那時我大概五歲
when I was about five.

781
00:54:46,633 --> 00:54:49,693
我的眼睛是到七歲時…才因為白喉失明的
I didn't lose my sight till I was seven. Diphtheria.

782
00:54:49,769 --> 00:54:52,067
你可以把刀子拿給我嗎？
Could you hand me that knife?

783
00:55:08,955 --> 00:55:13,392
我一直試著留住美洲獅的印象
I've always tried to hang on to what that cougar looked like.

784
00:55:14,394 --> 00:55:18,330
但是說實話，現在我腦袋裡的留下來的…
But by now, to tell the truth, what I see in my head...

785
00:55:18,431 --> 00:55:20,558
可能一點都不像美洲獅
is probably not in the least bit like a cougar.

786
00:55:20,633 --> 00:55:22,794
反而比較像驢子或山羊
It's more like a donkey or a goat.

787
00:55:22,902 --> 00:55:25,666
你知道有時候，我不確定是不是真的看見
You know, sometimes I'm not so sure I really saw him.

788
00:55:25,772 --> 00:55:28,570
也許只是我的想像
Maybe he's just something I dreamed up.

789
00:55:31,845 --> 00:55:33,608
你還好嗎？
You okay?

790
00:55:35,515 --> 00:55:37,676
你話不多，是不是？
You don't say much, do you?

791
00:55:38,117 --> 00:55:39,880
對，我想是
No, I guess not.

792
00:55:42,755 --> 00:55:47,351
讓我們說說別的，然後就結束，好嗎？
Let's talk about something and get it out of the way, okay?

793
00:55:57,170 --> 00:55:59,468
我可以聽得出來你…
I can hear that you've had...

794
00:56:00,507 --> 00:56:02,941
你動過軟顎手術
some kind of soft palate repair.

795
00:56:04,043 --> 00:56:07,672
但你說的我都聽得懂，因為你說得很清楚
But I understand you fine because you speak very well.

796
00:56:08,681 --> 00:56:11,809
如果你不想跟我說話，沒關係
If you don't want to talk to me, that's cool.

797
00:56:12,886 --> 00:56:15,514
但是我希望你跟我說，因為…
But I hope that you will, because...

798
00:56:16,856 --> 00:56:18,915
我知道，老是讓別人覺得…
I know what it's like to have people...

799
00:56:18,992 --> 00:56:21,620
你很奇怪是什麼樣的感覺
always thinking that you're different.

800
00:56:25,231 --> 00:56:26,789
很好
That's good.

801
00:56:29,669 --> 00:56:31,694
我可以摸你的臉嗎？
May I touch your face?

802
00:56:32,872 --> 00:56:35,864
我想知道你是在笑，還是在皺眉頭
I want to know if you're smiling or frowning.

803
00:56:35,975 --> 00:56:39,411
我想知道…我是不是應該閉嘴
I want to know whether I should just shut up or not.

804
00:56:49,989 --> 00:56:52,321
相信我，我在笑
Take my word that I'm smiling.

805
00:56:56,496 --> 00:56:58,020
我要走了
I have to go.

806
00:56:58,097 --> 00:57:00,463
如果我冒犯到你，我不是故意的
If I offended you, I didn't mean to.

807
00:57:00,533 --> 00:57:01,898
不
No.

808
00:57:08,841 --> 00:57:11,002
我到過他們家，可是我還是無法想像出…
F.B.I. Headquarters, Washington, D.C.

809
00:57:11,077 --> 00:57:12,977
傑柯比一家生前是什麼樣的人
WILL: I don't know what they were like.

810
00:57:13,046 --> 00:57:15,708
如果我可以看看他們一些私人的東西
It'd help if I could see some of their personal effects.

811
00:57:15,782 --> 00:57:18,580
日記、信件，你有這東西嗎？
Diaries, letters. Do you have those things?

812
00:57:18,685 --> 00:57:20,778
我有，我指的是除了…
I sure do. I mean, other than...

813
00:57:20,853 --> 00:57:24,779
除了一兩件奈爾傑柯比拿走要當紀念的東西之外
one or two little keepsakes Niles Jacobi got.

814
00:57:24,891 --> 00:57:28,088
那是傑柯比倖存的兒子，他和前妻生的？
That would be Mr. Jacobi's surviving son by his first wife?

815
00:57:28,194 --> 00:57:29,727
對，身為他們的法定代理人
Yes. As their executor, I keep all that stuff in the office...

816
00:57:29,744 --> 00:57:31,577
我把所有東西留在辦公室…

817
00:57:31,598 --> 00:57:35,557
包括一些值錢的小東西，直到遺囑公證之後
along with some of the smaller valuables, till after probate.

818
00:57:35,702 --> 00:57:38,535
但伯明翰警察局已經搜過所有的東西
But the Birmingham P.D.'s been all through it.

819
00:57:38,605 --> 00:57:41,199
你可以把那些東西寄給我嗎？
Could you pack those things and ship them up to me?

820
00:57:45,278 --> 00:57:48,406
我不喜歡這樣，我知道這樣很麻煩
I hate to ask. I know it's a pain in the ass.

821
00:57:50,917 --> 00:57:52,612
管他的…
Hell...

822
00:57:52,952 --> 00:57:56,080
遺囑公證的法官…是我的高爾夫老球友
probate judge is an old golfing buddy of mine.

823
00:57:57,490 --> 00:58:02,154
告訴我你會逮到那個畜牲
Son, just tell me you're gonna nail that son of a bitch.

824
00:58:02,328 --> 00:58:02,953
我們會盡力
We're doing our best.

825
00:58:04,797 --> 00:58:06,924
謝謝，麥考夫先生
Hey, thanks, Mr. Metcalf.

826
00:58:07,000 --> 00:58:09,092
萊克特的牢房裡藏了一張紙條
A note hidden in Lecter's cell. Sounds like a fan letter.

827
00:58:09,110 --> 00:58:10,092
似乎是仰慕者的信

828
00:58:10,103 --> 00:58:11,832
可能來自牙仙
Might've been mailed by the Tooth Fairy.

829
00:58:11,904 --> 00:58:13,428
他想要萊克特的認同
He wants Lecter's approval.

830
00:58:13,506 --> 00:58:15,838
他對你很好奇，他問了很多問題
He's curious about you. He's asking questions.

831
00:58:15,908 --> 00:58:17,671
我已經準備了一輛直升機
I've scrambled a chopper.

832
00:58:17,744 --> 00:58:19,268
萊克特知道了嗎？
Does Lecter know we have the note?

833
00:58:19,345 --> 00:58:21,540
還不知道，那是在例行的清潔工作中發現的
CRAWFORD: Not yet. It was found in a routine cleanup.

834
00:58:21,614 --> 00:58:23,047
他們不拆他的郵件？
WILL: They don't open his mail?

835
00:58:23,116 --> 00:58:25,016
要有搜索令，只能用X光檢查
CRAWFORD: Need a warrant. X-rays only.

836
00:58:25,084 --> 00:58:27,018
萊克特現在在哪裡？　　在禁閉室
WILL: Where's Lecter? CRAWFORD: The holding cage.

837
00:58:27,086 --> 00:58:28,553
他看得到牢房嗎？
WILL: Can he see his cell?

838
00:58:28,621 --> 00:58:31,112
看不到，但他幾乎被綁了半小時了
CRAWFORD: No. But he's been there almost half an hour.

839
00:58:31,190 --> 00:58:32,851
他很快就會發現事情不對勁
He'll soon start to wonder what's wrong.

840
00:58:32,925 --> 00:58:34,984
我們要爭取時間
We got to buy time, Jack.

841
00:58:38,031 --> 00:58:39,555
奇爾頓醫師   哪位？
CRAWFORD: Dr. Chilton. CHILTON: Yes?

842
00:58:39,632 --> 00:58:41,259
通知大樓管理處…
Call your building superintendent...

843
00:58:41,334 --> 00:58:43,165
或工程師，反正是負責人就行
or engineer, whoever's in charge.

844
00:58:43,236 --> 00:58:45,761
把萊克特牢房走廊的保險絲剪斷
Tell him to pull the circuit breakers on Lecter's hall.

845
00:58:45,838 --> 00:58:48,864
要工程人員帶著工具，穿過走道…
Have the super walk down the hall past the cell...

846
00:58:48,975 --> 00:58:49,964
經過牢房
carrying tools.

847
00:58:50,043 --> 00:58:54,446
他要很生氣、很著急，忙得沒空回答問題
He'll be in a hurry, pissed off, too busy to answer questions.

848
00:58:54,514 --> 00:58:58,111
而且不要忘記：不要碰那張紙條，行嗎？
And don't forget: Don't touch the note, okay?

849
00:58:58,284 --> 00:59:00,252
葛蘭姆就在路上
Graham's on his way.

850
00:59:00,453 --> 00:59:04,150
聽著！這是緊急狀況，我們會拿到一張紙條…
Listen up! We've got a note coming in on the fly...

851
00:59:04,257 --> 00:59:08,284
很可能來自牙仙，非常重要
possibly from the Tooth Fairy. Number One Priority.

852
00:59:08,761 --> 00:59:11,286
紙條必須在一小時內送回萊克特的牢房…
It has to go back to Lecter's cell within the hour...

853
00:59:11,364 --> 00:59:12,956
不准動手腳
unmarked.

854
00:59:13,032 --> 00:59:15,522
我們需要頭髮和纖維鑒驗部門…
We'll need Hair and Fiber, Latent Prints, then Documents.

855
00:59:15,542 --> 00:59:17,332
潛在指紋檢查和文件

856
00:59:17,837 --> 00:59:21,000
我會親自監督，大家現在就行動！
I'll walk it through myself. Let's go, people!

857
00:59:22,204 --> 00:59:24,195
[Dramatic instrumental music]

858
00:59:24,610 --> 00:59:28,548
我親愛的萊克特醫師：我想告訴你我很高興…
DOLARHYDE [Voice-over]: My dear Dr. Lecter.: I wanted to tell you...

859
00:59:28,548 --> 00:59:30,812
你對我有興趣
I'm delighted...

860
00:59:30,883 --> 00:59:35,183
當我知道你的反應時，我想…
that you've taken an interest in me.

861
00:59:32,014 --> 00:59:36,314
And when I learned of your vast correspondence, I thought.:

862
00:59:35,822 --> 00:59:38,620
「我敢嗎？」當然
"Dare I?" Of course I do.

863
00:59:40,693 --> 00:59:43,093
我不相信…你會告訴他們我是誰
I don't believe you'll tell them who I am.

864
00:59:43,162 --> 00:59:46,893
何況，我目前的軀體雖然是平凡的
Besides, what particular body I currently occupy is trivial.

865
00:59:46,999 --> 00:59:49,991
重要的是我即將蛻變
The important thing is what I am becoming.

866
00:59:50,503 --> 00:59:54,303
我知道…只有你可以瞭解這種轉型
I know that you alone can understand this transformation.

867
00:59:54,741 --> 00:59:57,676
有一些東西我很希望你能看見
I have some things I'd love to show you.

868
00:59:57,844 --> 01:00:01,302
如果情況許可，我希望能與你合作
If circumstances permit, I hope we can correspond.

869
01:00:02,381 --> 01:00:04,406
多年來我一直很景仰你…
I have admired you for years and have...

870
01:00:04,484 --> 01:00:06,748
我有你完整的剪報
a complete collection of your press notices.

871
01:00:06,853 --> 01:00:09,913
事實上，我認為他們對你的報導不公平
Actually, I think of them as unfair reviews.

872
01:00:10,690 --> 01:00:12,487
對我也是
As unfair as mine.

873
01:00:13,226 --> 01:00:16,855
他們喜歡亂取一些低俗的綽號，不是嗎？
They do like to sling demeaning nicknames, don't they?

874
01:00:17,163 --> 01:00:20,655
還有什麼比「牙仙」更不恰當的？
"The Tooth Fairy. " What could be more inappropriate?

875
01:00:21,100 --> 01:00:24,194
如果不是因為你也有同樣的遭遇…
It would shame me for you to read that, if I didn't know...

876
01:00:24,270 --> 01:00:27,034
我會因為你讀到這些報導覺得丟臉
you had suffered the same distortions in the press.

877
01:00:27,106 --> 01:00:29,734
我受夠了這棟該死的的建築！
I'm fed up with this bloody stupid building!

878
01:00:29,842 --> 01:00:31,207
每天都有東西壞掉
Every day something breaking.

879
01:00:31,277 --> 01:00:34,110
我發誓，他們必須要把整個地方拆掉
SUPER: I swear they ought to tear the whole fucking place down.

880
01:00:34,213 --> 01:00:37,205
我們還有多少時間？　　最多十分鐘
- How much longer do we have? - Ten minutes, max.

881
01:00:37,283 --> 01:00:39,080
解答指引…
BOWMAN: Instructions for answering...

882
01:00:39,185 --> 01:00:41,119
可能就是被萊克特撕掉的部份
were probably in the section Lecter tore out.

883
01:00:41,187 --> 01:00:43,587
為什麼不乾脆整個丟掉？
Why not just throw the whole note away?

884
01:00:43,689 --> 01:00:45,350
裡面全是讚美
It was full of compliments.

885
01:00:45,424 --> 01:00:47,756
他捨不得丟掉
He couldn't bear to part with them.

886
01:00:48,958 --> 01:00:52,416
[Suspenseful instrumental music]

887
01:00:51,364 --> 01:00:53,798
現在我們讓我們合在一起看看
Now we can mash just a little.

888
01:00:55,201 --> 01:00:56,896
你真狡猾
You're so sly.

889
01:00:58,604 --> 01:01:00,572
但是我也不輸你
BOWMAN: But so am I.

890
01:01:01,374 --> 01:01:04,468
苯胺染料、彩色墨水在紅外線之下是透明的
Aniline dyes and colored inks are transparent to infrared.

891
01:01:04,577 --> 01:01:07,705
這有可能是「T」，這裡、還有那裡
These could be the tips of "T's" here and here.

892
01:01:07,880 --> 01:01:10,747
句尾是「P」，也有可能是「R」
On the end, that's a "P, " or possibly an "R."

893
01:01:10,817 --> 01:01:13,718
也許這裡…是他告訴萊克特怎麼響應他的地方
Maybe this is where he's telling Lecter how to answer him.

894
01:01:13,786 --> 01:01:16,152
只有一個方法可以繼續這樣的對話…
There's only one way to carry on a conversation...

895
01:01:16,222 --> 01:01:17,416
就是一明一暗
that's one-way blind.

896
01:01:17,490 --> 01:01:19,424
出版品，等一下
Publication. Wait a minute.

897
01:01:19,492 --> 01:01:21,153
我們知道他讀《傳聞報》
We know this guy reads the Tattler.

898
01:01:21,227 --> 01:01:22,819
他在紙條裡提到，是嗎？
That's in his note, right?

899
01:01:22,895 --> 01:01:24,988
牙仙，報社起的綽號
The Tooth Fairy, they made that up.

900
01:01:25,097 --> 01:01:27,929
《傳聞報》就是三個「T」和一個「R」
BOWMAN: Three "T's" and an "R" in "Tattler."

901
01:01:27,967 --> 01:01:30,094
你怎麼利用小報傳消息？
How do you communicate through a tabloid?

902
01:01:30,169 --> 01:01:32,933
用什麼？新聞報導   徵人啟事
- You got what? News stories. - Personals.

903
01:01:33,005 --> 01:01:35,872
也許他希望萊克特透過徵人啟事回答他的問題？
Maybe he wants Lecter to answer him through the personals?

904
01:01:35,942 --> 01:01:38,502
有可能   我們必須在下一期出刊前…
- That could be it. - We need proofs of the pages...

905
01:01:38,578 --> 01:01:40,068
看到這些徵人啟事！
before the next Tattler's published!

906
01:01:40,146 --> 01:01:41,204
我負責！
CRAWFORD: I'm on it!

907
01:01:41,280 --> 01:01:43,680
調查員葛蘭姆引起了我的興趣
DOLARHYDE: Investigator Graham interests me.

908
01:01:43,783 --> 01:01:46,149
他不是普通的偵探對不對？
Not your standard gumshoe, is he?

909
01:01:46,252 --> 01:01:47,241
更有警覺
More alert.

910
01:01:47,320 --> 01:01:49,220
有目的的搜尋
Purposeful looking.

911
01:01:49,589 --> 01:01:52,490
你應該叫他不要插手
You should have taught him not to meddle.

912
01:01:53,092 --> 01:01:54,753
原諒我寫在捲筒衛生紙上
Forgive the stationery.

913
01:01:54,827 --> 01:01:57,352
我這樣做是因為…如果你需要把它吞下去…
I chose it because it'll dissolve very quickly...

914
01:01:57,430 --> 01:01:59,990
它會很快溶化
if you should have to swallow it.

915
01:02:00,266 --> 01:02:04,202
如果有你的回音，下次我會寄濕的東西給你
If I hear from you, next time I might send you something wet.

916
01:02:06,706 --> 01:02:08,799
下次再聊，親愛的醫師…
Until then, dear Doctor...

917
01:02:08,875 --> 01:02:10,775
我是你最…
I remain your most...

918
01:02:10,943 --> 01:02:12,843
熱情的仰慕者
avid fan.

919
01:02:13,809 --> 01:02:17,301
[Suspenseful instrumental music]

920
01:02:32,965 --> 01:02:35,297
《傳聞報》接了一個廣告訂單，屬名666…
CRAWFORD: The Tattler got an ad order signed 666...

921
01:02:35,368 --> 01:02:37,336
信封上是巴爾的摩的郵戳
Baltimore postmark on the envelope.

922
01:02:37,403 --> 01:02:39,303
預計在在今天下午刊登出來
It's set to run this afternoon.

923
01:02:39,372 --> 01:02:42,864
芝加哥正把廣告內容傳真過來
Chicago field office is sending the text through now.

924
01:02:45,912 --> 01:02:47,937
「親愛的朝聖者」　　就是這個
- "Dear Pilgrim." - That's it.

925
01:02:48,014 --> 01:02:50,244
當萊克特談起他時，稱他朝聖者
Lecter called him a pilgrim when we talked.

926
01:02:50,316 --> 01:02:53,649
「你給我榮耀，你非常完美」，天啊！
"You honor me. You're very beautiful." Christ!

927
01:02:54,186 --> 01:02:56,347
「為了你的安全，我獻給你100個祝福
"I offer 100 prayers for your safety.

928
01:02:56,422 --> 01:02:59,414
「在《聖經：約翰》6：22、8：16…
"Find help in John 6:22, 8:16...

929
01:02:59,492 --> 01:03:01,426
「9：1，《路加福音》1：7」
"9:1, Luke 1:7."

930
01:03:01,494 --> 01:03:03,155
密碼   一定是
- Code. - Has to be.

931
01:03:05,665 --> 01:03:09,601
如果能解碼的話，離刊登訊息還有19分鐘
We've got 19 minutes to get in a message if we can break this.

932
01:03:09,702 --> 01:03:12,000
《傳聞報》不可能等我們太久
The Tattler can't hold its presses any longer.

933
01:03:12,071 --> 01:03:13,038
很簡單
It's simple.

934
01:03:13,105 --> 01:03:15,665
他們只要能照顧到一般讀者
They only needed cover against casual readers.

935
01:03:15,775 --> 01:03:17,675
我想是書本密碼   密碼？
- I'm thinking it's a book code. - Code?

936
01:03:17,743 --> 01:03:19,040
第一個數字…
The first numeral...

937
01:03:19,111 --> 01:03:20,942
「100」也許是書的頁碼
"100 prayers," may be the page number.

938
01:03:21,013 --> 01:03:23,413
之後的數字可能代表行或字，但是是什麼書？
The numbers after could be line and letter. But what book?

939
01:03:23,482 --> 01:03:25,949
《聖經》？　　不，是《加拉太書》1：52
- Bible? - No, he's got "Galatians 15:2."

940
01:03:25,952 --> 01:03:27,476
但《加拉太書》只有六章
It has only six chapters.

941
01:03:27,553 --> 01:03:29,953
和《喬納》6：8一樣，《喬納》也只有四章
Same with "Jonah 6:8." It has four chapters.

942
01:03:30,022 --> 01:03:31,284
他不是用聖經
He wasn't using a Bible.

943
01:03:31,390 --> 01:03:34,018
牙仙有提到這本書
Then the Tooth Fairy named the book to use.

944
01:03:34,093 --> 01:03:37,028
就在紙條裡，被萊克特撕掉的那部份
He specified it in his note, in the part Lecter tore out.

945
01:03:37,096 --> 01:03:38,961
可能就是這樣
BOWMAN: It would appear so.

946
01:03:39,031 --> 01:03:42,023
為什麼不利用精神病中心對萊克特逼供…
What about sweating Lecter? In a mental hospital...

947
01:03:42,101 --> 01:03:43,659
可以用藥…　　不
- I would think drugs... - No.

948
01:03:43,736 --> 01:03:46,534
三年前，他們對他用過安眠藥，想知道…
They tried sodium amytal on him three years ago, to find out...

949
01:03:46,639 --> 01:03:48,573
普林斯頓學生的屍體埋在哪裡
where he buried the Princeton student.

950
01:03:48,641 --> 01:03:50,666
他們挖出來的是一個食譜
He gave them a recipe for dip.

951
01:03:50,743 --> 01:03:52,836
如果我們逼他，就失掉了一個管道
If we sweat him, we lose the connection.

952
01:03:52,912 --> 01:03:54,846
如果牙仙選的書是…
If the Tooth Fairy picked the book...

953
01:03:54,914 --> 01:03:57,348
是他知道萊克特牢房裡也有的書
he knew Lecter would have it in his cell.

954
01:03:57,416 --> 01:03:58,908
我們可以拿到他書的清單嗎？
- Can we get a list of his books? - From Chilton, maybe.

955
01:03:58,916 --> 01:04:00,448
也許從奇爾頓那裡拿得到

956
01:04:00,486 --> 01:04:03,478
不！等等！當藍肯和威靈漢搜索牢房時…
No! Wait! Rankin and Willingham, when they tossed his cell...

957
01:04:03,589 --> 01:04:06,490
拍了拍立得好將東西放回原位
took Polaroids so they could put everything back in place.

958
01:04:06,592 --> 01:04:09,288
要他們把書架的照片帶來！
Ask them to meet me with pictures of his bookshelves!

959
01:04:09,395 --> 01:04:11,625
帶去哪裡？　　圖書館！
CRAWFORD: Where? BOWMAN: The Library!

960
01:04:15,001 --> 01:04:17,265
萊克特的訊息還沒解出來，就登在報紙上…
I'm leery of letting Lecter's message run...

961
01:04:17,336 --> 01:04:19,566
我有不安的感覺
without knowing what it says.

962
01:04:20,673 --> 01:04:23,471
讓這則廣告註銷去，但我們繼續譯碼
I say let this one run. We keep working on the code.

963
01:04:23,576 --> 01:04:26,340
至少這樣能鼓勵牙仙再一次和他連絡
At least it'll encourage the Fairy to contact him again.

964
01:04:26,445 --> 01:04:29,243
萬一這不是鼓勵他寫信，而是要他做別的事呢？
What if it encourages him to do something besides write?

965
01:04:29,315 --> 01:04:31,476
我和你一樣不喜歡這樣
I don't like this any better than you.

966
01:04:32,284 --> 01:04:34,514
但這是我們最好的機會
But it's our best shot.

967
01:04:36,122 --> 01:04:39,318
（國家傳聞報大樓，伊利裡諾伊州，芝加哥）
[Dramatic instrumental music]

968
01:04:37,753 --> 01:04:40,051
National Tattler Building, Chicago, Il

969
01:04:52,138 --> 01:04:54,003
（親愛的朝聖者）

970
01:04:54,574 --> 01:04:57,604
（國會圖書館，華盛頓特區）
Library of Congress, Washington, D.C.

971
01:04:58,807 --> 01:05:02,299
[Eerie instrumental music]

972
01:05:11,357 --> 01:05:13,257
哦，我的天！
BOWMAN: Oh, my God!

973
01:05:18,364 --> 01:05:19,296
喂？
Hello?

974
01:05:19,365 --> 01:05:21,629
傑克，我是羅伊布朗曼，我解出密碼了
Jack, it's Lloyd Bowman. I solved the code.

975
01:05:21,700 --> 01:05:23,497
你有必要立刻知道是什麼
You need to know what it says right now.

976
01:05:23,569 --> 01:05:24,729
好，羅伊
Okay, Lloyd.

977
01:05:24,804 --> 01:05:28,069
它是說：「葛蘭姆家在佛羅里達的馬拉松」
It says, "Graham home, Marathon, Florida.

978
01:05:28,207 --> 01:05:30,698
「拯救你自己，殺了他們全家」
"Save yourself. Kill them all."

979
01:05:32,411 --> 01:05:34,971
喂？　　布朗曼剛才解出密碼
WILL: Yeah? CRAWFORD: Bowman just broke the code.

980
01:05:35,414 --> 01:05:37,780
上面怎麼說？　　我等一下就告訴你
- What does it say? - I'll tell you in a second.

981
01:05:37,850 --> 01:05:39,977
現在聽我說，一切沒事
Now, listen to me. Everything is okay.

982
01:05:40,052 --> 01:05:42,816
我會處理，等我的電話，我會告訴你
I've taken care of it. Stay on the phone when I tell you.

983
01:05:42,888 --> 01:05:43,980
現在告訴我
Tell me now.

984
01:05:44,056 --> 01:05:45,956
萊克特把你家地址給那個畜生
Lecter gave the bastard your home address.

985
01:05:46,025 --> 01:05:47,458
等等
CRAWFORD: Wait.

986
01:05:54,296 --> 01:05:55,126
[Faint thump]

987
01:05:57,266 --> 01:06:00,258
[Door opening]

988
01:06:00,669 --> 01:06:04,332
[Harrowing instrumental music]

989
01:06:14,954 --> 01:06:16,512
媽？
Mom?

990
01:06:28,134 --> 01:06:30,227
頭低下來，女士
AGENT [Shouting]: Head down, ma'am.

991
01:06:31,433 --> 01:06:34,925
[Dramatic instrumental music]

992
01:06:49,017 --> 01:06:52,509
[Tender instrumental music]

993
01:06:56,428 --> 01:06:57,986
你變成他的目標了嗎？
MOLLY: Is he after you now?

994
01:06:58,063 --> 01:07:00,554
不，萊克特才建議他這樣做
WILL: No, Lecter just suggested it to him.

995
01:07:02,735 --> 01:07:05,101
我不喜歡這樣，莫莉
I hate this, Molly.

996
01:07:05,938 --> 01:07:07,565
對不起
I'm sorry.

997
01:07:09,175 --> 01:07:11,769
感覺很病態   我知道
- It's a sick feeling. - I know it is.

998
01:07:11,977 --> 01:07:13,444
但是你在這裡很安全
But you'll be safe here.

999
01:07:13,512 --> 01:07:15,412
這裡是克勞佛弟弟的
Crawford's brother owns this place.

1000
01:07:15,481 --> 01:07:17,506
沒有人知道你在這裡
No one in the world knows you're here.

1001
01:07:17,616 --> 01:07:20,176
我希望很快可以不用再談到克勞佛
I'd just as soon not talk about Crawford.

1002
01:07:20,753 --> 01:07:24,621
你的誘餌是什麼？　　有時候我用蟲
AGENT: What are you using as bait? JOSH: Sometimes I use worms.

1003
01:07:24,757 --> 01:07:26,520
你喜歡嗎？
AGENT: You like those?

1004
01:07:41,307 --> 01:07:43,036
在黃色的檔案夾下面…
Beneath the yellow folder...

1005
01:07:43,108 --> 01:07:44,871
你會找到最近的拒絕聲明…
you'll find your latest rejection slip...

1006
01:07:44,944 --> 01:07:46,468
夾在檔案裡面
from the archives.

1007
01:07:46,545 --> 01:07:50,106
這是不小心和我的檔案郵件一起送來的
LECTER: It was brought to me by mistake with some of my archives mail.

1008
01:07:50,182 --> 01:07:52,980
我沒注意就把它打開來看
I'm afraid I opened it without looking.

1009
01:07:53,319 --> 01:07:54,946
對不起
Sorry.

1010
01:07:59,992 --> 01:08:03,723
我想我們要把萊克特醫師的馬桶移走
I think we'll remove Dr. Lecter's toilet seat.

1011
01:08:08,430 --> 01:08:10,421
[Gunshots]

1012
01:08:20,909 --> 01:08:24,572
[Dramatic instrumental music]

1013
01:08:27,486 --> 01:08:29,420
亞特蘭大警局逮到他
CRAWFORD: Atlanta P.D. nailed him.

1014
01:08:29,488 --> 01:08:31,456
他持假FBI證件…
He had a fake Bureau ID...

